# SLPP NY Inauguration Website — Photo Checklist

Drop files into this `photos` folder using these **exact** filenames (all lowercase,
hyphens, no spaces). Recommended size: 800×800px square for portraits, 1200×750px
landscape for landmarks/gallery/boat ride, JPEG at ~80% quality, 100–300KB each.

